description: Try our easy to follow D'Orsogna Premium Honey Ham Off The Bone, Cheese & Zucchini Muffins recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: D'Orsogna Premium Honey Ham Off The Bone, Cheese & Zucchini Muffins Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 170g jarrah honey ham off the bone, chopped (from the deli)

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200Â°C. Line a 12-hole medium muffin tray with paper cases. Set aside 30g chopped ham. Squeeze liquid from zucchini.
Place zucchini, remaining ham, parsley and flour in a medium bowl and combine. Season with pepper.

Mix cottage cheese and egg together. Stir into zucchini mixture until combined. Divide mixture evenly between paper cases, scatter with reserved ham and parmesan. Bake for 25 minutes until golden brown and cooked through. Serve.
